{"tid":1834983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：回應暴徒政治訴求並非審慎方法","createTime":"2020-01-22T15:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T15:51:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfa332e5c257c26fab9bd1a50b69dbfa23b61c3","tid":1834983,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥正在瑞士達沃斯出席世界經濟論壇年會。<br />\n<br />\n她在會上表示，若將香港的示威簡化為爭取民主及長期自由，可能是低估局勢；同樣地，若只因示威者或暴徒提出政治訴求，政府就要回應，她認為不是確保香港未來及公眾利益的審慎方法。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥早前也在當地接受傳媒訪問，重申自己不會辭職，又指整場社會事件中，沒有人因警方行動而死亡，若然警方執法有失當會受到法律制裁，重申監警會正展開調查，不會成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504286-20200122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504286-20200122.htm&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=d4f32379\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504286-20200122.htm&h=15e016d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504286-20200122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7e25b4181e0f505fea904bfe8de1db2162f0d783","tid":1834983,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78abf46cb4ce5eded2737dae2f61cfa4075219a1","tid":1834983,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢真係當鬼佬唔知香港發生咩事"}]}